commit.message:

	* config/i386/32/sfp-machine.h (FP_HANDLE_EXCEPTIONS) [FP_EX_INVALID]:
	Initialize f with 0.0.
	* config/i386/32/sfp-machine.h (FP_HANDLE_EXCEPTIONS) [FP_EX_INVALID]:
